<bug>
	<id>95845</id>
	<title>Use CommandInfoProvider to receive UNO command labels/tooltips</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">To receive labels/tooltips from UNO commands, different methods are used across the codebase.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">The preferred way is to use CommandInfoProvider (svtools/source/misc/commandinfoprovider.cxx).</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">The task is to replace usages of DefaultCommandDescriptionProvider (forms/source/helper/commanddescriptionprovider.cxx) and theUICommandDescription (opengrok.libreoffice.org/search?q=theUICommandDescription) with CommandInfoProvider.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
